<Fragment slot="intro">
<p>Newport Beach is the most coastal city we service in Orange County — and the salt air here works from multiple directions depending on where you live. Newport Bay surrounds Balboa Island on all sides. The Back Bay reaches into the eastern part of the city. The Pacific runs the full western edge from Corona del Mar to Newport Coast. Gas dryer flex connectors corrode faster here than in any other OC city we service. A connector that lasts 7 years in Irvine lasts 3 years on Balboa Island — and on some Lido Isle properties, 2 years. The moisture sensor mineral deposit problem is also specific to Newport Beach: ocean minerals in the air settle on the sensor bars of DLEX3570 and DLGX3571 models over time, causing false "dry" readings that end cycles early. We know every Newport Beach neighbourhood by its salt air character. Call before 2pm for best same-day availability.</p>
