<p><strong>LG Signature service — Newport Coast ($320–480).</strong> Drum bearing, steam system diagnostics, ThinQ error codes. Full premium protocol. Gate coordination, text confirmation.</p>

<p><strong>Stacked unit access — Balboa Island and Mariner's Mile condos.</strong> 30–45 minutes, no surcharge. Foil transition replaced every time.</p>

